  <brief_title>A Study to Evaluate the Impact of Maintaining Hemoglobin Levels in Anemic Patients With Carcinoma of the Cervix</brief_title>
  <acronym>HOSTT</acronym>
  <official_title>A Phase III Study to Evaluate the Impact of Maintaining Haemoglobin Levels Above 120g/L Verses Above 100g/L in Anaemic Patients With Carcinoma of the Cervix Receiving Concurrent Cisplatin and Radiation Therapy</official_title>
