  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Previously untreated cervix cancer

          -  FIGO stage IB2, II, IIIB, IVA

          -  Suitable for treatment with radical intent using concurrent cisplatin and pelvic
             radiation

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Hemoglobin level above 125g/L

          -  Lower one-third vaginal involvement

          -  Para-aortic lymphadenopathy
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
